		"description": "## Welcome to the Bookstore API (version 1.0.0).\n\n**Endpoints:**\n\n**Authors:**\n\n- Get all authors: `GET /authors`\n    \n- Get one author: `GET /authors/:id`\n    \n- Create an author: `POST /authors`\n    \n- Update an author: `PUT /authors/:id`\n    \n- Delete an author: `DELETE /authors/:id`\n    \n- Get books by an author: `GET /authors/:id/books`\n    \n\n**Books:**\n\n- Get all books: `GET /books`\n    \n- Get all books by a specific author: `GET /books?author=:authorId`\n    \n- Get one book: `GET /books/:id`\n    \n- Create a book: `POST /books`\n    \n- Update a book: `PUT /books/:id`\n    \n- Delete a book: `DELETE /books/:id`",
